<h1>

PyPackIT Test1 Contributing Guidelines

</h1>

<p align="justify">
   Welcome to the <em>PyPackIT Test1</em> community!
   We are excited to have you here,
   and grateful that you are considering contributing.
   PyPackIT Test1 is a free and open-source project that evolves with the needs of its users,
   and can only grow through the help of great members like you.
</p>

<h2>

How To Contribute

</h2>

<p align="justify">
   To keep all our project documentation organized and easy to find, the complete
   <a href="https://AAriam.github.io/PyPackIT-Test1/contribute">contribution guide</a> is hosted on our website.
</p>
